title: 59 Simone De La Rue: Bringing Joy to Business and Fitness to Work with Top Celebrities
description: This week on the School of Greatness podcast, Simone de la Rue joins to talk about her astonishing career as a dancer as well as how she built a thriving business with no previous knowledge of business. It's an amazing story.
author: podcast@schoolofgreatness.com (Lewis Howes)
